{"tid":1750560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以爲自己沒得投票既人入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-24T12:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T14:04:06.000Z","uid":239655,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"496f2dde060173770f57c351de536842f902ee9d","tid":1750560,"uid":239655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:31:40.000Z","msg":"有好多巴打可能今年沒登記做選民以爲自己沒得投票，其實只要你夠18歲辦理身份證既時候會自動登記做選民，只係你地吾記得左呢回事。<br />\n有一個好簡單既step check你係咪選民:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=e698b4e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n入呢個網站輸入身份證信息就可以check到是否為登記選民，30秒完成驗證。<br />\n利申本人就係其中一個例子，唔想其他巴打因爲以爲自己沒得投票而遺憾終身。<br />\n可能類似既post已經早就出過，可選擇不推文回復或者上一頁，最後都係一句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cf2f79bc3c065eba2589f189b6a1040d03acf93b","tid":1750560,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69dd5778ec6791a27913991e02e95333edd22f44","tid":1750560,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ddeb109e6794ff4fa1887ddb96a58dcaf6813bfc","tid":1750560,"uid":221894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3644ed90e5de365bee5467933e83a5b6f86489f5","tid":1750560,"uid":239655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"40b122a88ae31eb85a0fabb71c8588471e40b6fa","tid":1750560,"uid":239655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:36:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72b06cd453053b42097bfc967e16037d366726a0","tid":1750560,"uid":239655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"